ygData.messageBody:
Mystic Alliance is up on Rodcet. If you would like to join just send a tell to Fentus, Genesius, Damarr, Taren, Vesuka, Siza, or Ssauric.
Just mention the list for an instant invite.

RoB
Genesius Faywood 31 Ranger
Siza 15 SK
